-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------- Eliminazione delle tabelle --------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DROP TABLE ratings;
DROP TABLE keywords;